name: Apollo
description:
A photorealistic merge that does very well at portraits and closeup shots.

Works with both male and female characters but seems to be better at female characters.

Recommended settings:

  • Steps: 20-25

  • Sampler: Euler a or DPM++ 2M Karras

  • CFG scale: 4-7

  • Size: 512x768 or 512x512

  • Denoising strength: 0.45-0.5

  • Hires upscale: 2

  • Upscaler: 4x-UltraSharp

No VAE required.
